          μ arrivalRate w ρ r hrate_measurable hw_integrable_acceptAll
          htime_integrable_acceptAll hlambda hρ_optimal hρ_reward_eq⟩

/--
Lemma 4, source-facing measurable version.  Theorem 1 supplies an optimal
